1
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:10,961
♪Love's little quiz
takes seven parts sweet♪

2
00:00:10,962 --> 00:00:13,559
♪And three parts bitter,
till you and I meet♪

3
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:17,159
♪I pretend I'm not there,
but secretly stay♪

4
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:26,399
♪Waiting for you♪

5
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:31,400
♪We've got so many
romantic dreams to unfold♪

6
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:36,224
♪Finally hearing
the I love you I long to hold♪

7
00:00:36,225 --> 00:00:39,839
♪Falling fast
into the swirl of your eyes♪

8
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:42,399
♪It's just too tempting, so tempting♪

9
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,499
♪Never could I have guessed♪

10
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:46,499
♪My heart's rhythm♪

11
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,632
♪How beautiful it is, meeting you♪

12
00:01:02,975 --> 00:01:05,961
=Late to Love=
(Adapted from "My Husband Is A Billionaire!")

13
00:01:05,962 --> 00:01:08,899
=Episode 23=

14
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:10,618
What I can share right now is

15
00:01:10,619 --> 00:01:13,258
that as the new drug
passes FDA approval,

16
00:01:13,259 --> 00:01:15,338
the current state of Alzheimer's care

17
00:01:15,339 --> 00:01:17,218
is going to see a massive breakthrough.

18
00:01:17,219 --> 00:01:19,058
We can fully foresee

19
00:01:19,059 --> 00:01:21,218
countless families
being brought back together

20
00:01:21,219 --> 00:01:23,579
and so much heartbreak finally healed.

21
00:01:23,580 --> 00:01:25,019
From day one,

22
00:01:25,020 --> 00:01:26,138
United Pharma has never been

23
00:01:26,139 --> 00:01:27,459
just about making a profit.

24
00:01:27,460 --> 00:01:28,659
Bringing hope to the world

25
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:31,299
is the true purpose
of a pharmaceutical company.

26
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:33,379
We just received a breaking news update.

27
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:35,498
A teaser for a new paper
by the medical genius Dr. X

28
00:01:35,499 --> 00:01:36,698
directly targets NIT-33,

29
00:01:36,699 --> 00:01:38,379
citing major safety risks.

30
00:01:38,619 --> 00:01:40,459
The finger is pointing
right at Ye Pharmaceutical.

31
00:01:40,460 --> 00:01:41,179
Miss Ye,

32
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:42,179
is there really an issue

33
00:01:42,180 --> 00:01:43,659
with NIT-33?

34
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:45,340
Please give us a straight answer.

35
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:47,778
As professional reporters,

36
00:01:47,779 --> 00:01:49,379
you should have the basic

37
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:50,858
ability to spot fake news.

38
00:01:50,859 --> 00:01:52,218
But right now overseas...

39
00:01:52,219 --> 00:01:55,179
The interview ends here.

40
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:22,218
Huo Zichen, you useless loser.

41
00:02:22,219 --> 00:02:22,899
I thought you said

42
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:24,539
you found Xu Nange.

43
00:02:24,659 --> 00:02:26,699
Didn't you say you'd stop her
from publishing the paper?

44
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:28,218
Look at the trending list right now.

45
00:02:28,219 --> 00:02:29,739
We got played.

46
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:31,618
It was all a setup by Huo Beiyan.

47
00:02:31,619 --> 00:02:32,378
He knew that we'd

48
00:02:32,379 --> 00:02:33,299
focus all our attention

49
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,859
on Xu Nange.

50
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:37,338
Even my uncle willingly became his pawn.

51
00:02:37,339 --> 00:02:39,058
What a smooth move.

52
00:02:39,059 --> 00:02:39,979
He chose

53
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:41,179
to throw the wedding right now

54
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:42,819
just to deliver the final blow.

55
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:44,658
Once Xu Nange takes the stage

56
00:02:44,659 --> 00:02:46,098
and goes public as Dr. X

57
00:02:46,099 --> 00:02:48,299
to expose the truth about NIT-33,

58
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:49,859
it's game over for us.

59
00:02:49,860 --> 00:02:52,139
What's the point
of talking about this now?

60
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:54,299
Once that paper drops officially,

61
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,058
I'm going to prison.

62
00:02:56,059 --> 00:02:57,658
I don't care how you do it.

63
00:02:57,659 --> 00:02:59,058
You need to find

64
00:02:59,059 --> 00:03:00,299
Xu Nange right now.

65
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,739
Destroy her research.

66
00:03:01,740 --> 00:03:02,699
It's too late.

67
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:04,220
No, it's not.

68
00:03:04,819 --> 00:03:05,658
If Xu Nange

69
00:03:05,659 --> 00:03:07,579
loses her safety net with Huo Beiyan,

70
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:09,099
I don't believe

71
00:03:09,260 --> 00:03:11,460
she'll keep hiding out.

72
00:03:13,339 --> 00:03:14,538
Stop hesitating.

73
00:03:14,539 --> 00:03:16,539
Make a move on Beiyan.

74
00:03:45,659 --> 00:03:46,580
Mr. Huo,

75
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,379
there's a car tailing us.

76
00:03:53,659 --> 00:03:54,539
Just pull over.

77
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:55,780
Alright.

78
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:16,059
Mr. Huo,

79
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,739
why don't you step out for a chat?

80
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:22,139
Mr. Huo,

81
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,499
Mr. Zichen wants to see you.

82
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,139
Thanks for the effort.

83
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,940
Bringing out a whole crew
just to get me.

84
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:33,580
I'll go with you.

85
00:04:44,739 --> 00:04:45,820
Mr. Huo!

86
00:05:15,099 --> 00:05:16,059
Mr. Zichen,

87
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,220
he's here.

88
00:05:19,380 --> 00:05:20,380
Beiyan,

89
00:05:20,859 --> 00:05:22,580
we're meeting here again.

90
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:24,459
You used to spend

91
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:25,940
a ton of time hanging out here.

92
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:29,260
Yeah.

93
00:05:29,419 --> 00:05:30,780
I just never thought

94
00:05:31,739 --> 00:05:33,260
we'd meet like this.

95
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,580
Look, Beiyan.

96
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:41,220
I won't beat around the bush.

97
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:43,858
Hand Xu Nange over to me.

98
00:05:43,859 --> 00:05:45,859
There's still a way to fix this.

99
00:05:46,099 --> 00:05:47,820
It's not too late for you

100
00:05:48,739 --> 00:05:50,140
to turn around now.

101
00:05:50,979 --> 00:05:52,220
Turn around?

102
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,179
Turn around to what?

103
00:05:55,539 --> 00:05:56,619
Go back to the company

104
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:58,019
and keep playing the part

105
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:59,579
of the second heir with zero power?

106
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:00,499
Or keep being

107
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:01,819
the stupid cousin

108
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:04,098
you play like a violin?

109
00:06:04,099 --> 00:06:04,699
Did you think

110
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:06,099
I was happy living like that?

111
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:09,978
So what?

112
00:06:09,979 --> 00:06:11,139
You think abducting me,

113
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:12,418
tearing the family apart,

114
00:06:12,419 --> 00:06:14,299
and wrecking the company
will make you happy?

115
00:06:26,779 --> 00:06:27,899
You make it sound

116
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,419
so easy.

117
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,299
Yeah.

118
00:06:33,739 --> 00:06:35,700
As long as I've been by your side,

119
00:06:36,339 --> 00:06:38,019
nobody ever noticed me.

120
00:06:38,020 --> 00:06:40,179
Everyone only had eyes for you,

121
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:43,538
the brilliant, successful Huo Beiyan.

122
00:06:43,539 --> 00:06:45,299
Who ever cares about how I felt?

123
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:47,220
And now,

124
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:50,979
you're even trying
to steal the woman I love.

125
00:06:55,659 --> 00:06:57,019
I just wanted to prove to her

126
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:58,380
that I've become a better person.

127
00:06:58,659 --> 00:07:00,820
But you wouldn't
even give me that chance.

128
00:07:01,299 --> 00:07:02,979
I spent four years abroad.

129
00:07:03,339 --> 00:07:05,299
Do you have any idea how hard I worked?

130
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:09,739
Beiyan,

131
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:13,179
I looked up to you.

132
00:07:13,580 --> 00:07:16,220
I spent every moment
trying to be just like you.

133
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:19,139
But what did I find

134
00:07:19,140 --> 00:07:20,739
when I came back home?

135
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:23,499
A carefully orchestrated lie!

136
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:26,139
A contract that completely crushed

137
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:28,419
all my effort
and hard work into the dirt!

138
00:07:37,580 --> 00:07:38,820
Zichen.

139
00:07:39,620 --> 00:07:41,260
That was an accident.

140
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,858
I admit

141
00:07:42,859 --> 00:07:45,298
that I kept it from you,
but I only did it because...

142
00:07:45,299 --> 00:07:46,380
Enough!

143
00:07:49,979 --> 00:07:52,019
Stop trying
to take the moral high ground.

144
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:54,900
You are the ones
who forced me down this path.

145
00:08:04,299 --> 00:08:05,619
Beiyan,

146
00:08:05,979 --> 00:08:07,340
we're cousins.

147
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:10,179
Don't let things get too ugly.

148
00:08:14,659 --> 00:08:17,298
I have all the time in the world today
to let you think things over.

149
00:08:17,299 --> 00:08:18,538
I just wonder

150
00:08:18,539 --> 00:08:20,179
if you can handle what comes next.

151
00:08:39,459 --> 00:08:40,460
Spit it out.

152
00:08:40,699 --> 00:08:42,180
Where is Xu Nange?

153
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:50,019
Tell me where Xu Nange is.

154
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:52,340
Where the hell is she?

155
00:08:58,299 --> 00:08:59,619
If you're going to hit me,

156
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,700
just do it.

157
00:09:03,659 --> 00:09:05,580
Do you honestly think I won't?

158
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:08,899
Even if you kill me today,

159
00:09:10,059 --> 00:09:11,619
I'm still your cousin.

160
00:09:33,419 --> 00:09:34,420
Zichen.

161
00:09:35,659 --> 00:09:36,660
Zichen.

162
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:40,540
Don't let Ye Xin make a fool out of us.

163
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:51,379
(Sorry.)

164
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:53,938
(The number
you have dialed is not reachable.)

165
00:09:53,939 --> 00:09:55,578
(Please try again later.)

166
00:09:55,579 --> 00:09:56,580
(Sorry.)

167
00:09:57,579 --> 00:09:58,578
What's going on?

168
00:09:58,579 --> 00:10:00,060
Where is Beiyan?

169
00:10:00,699 --> 00:10:03,099
Mrs. Huo, Mr. Huo is tied up
with some personal matters.

170
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:04,818
He probably can't get to his phone.

171
00:10:04,819 --> 00:10:05,859
What could possibly

172
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:07,178
be more important right now?

173
00:10:07,179 --> 00:10:08,979
He won't even pick up my calls.

174
00:10:10,819 --> 00:10:11,899
He's really fine.

175
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:13,019
He's just worried that someone

176
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,139
might come after you.

177
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:16,220
That's why he sent me to protect you.

178
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,979
Protect me?

179
00:10:18,579 --> 00:10:20,058
Tell me the truth.

180
00:10:20,059 --> 00:10:21,219
Where is he?

181
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,779
Why did you really come here?

182
00:10:23,299 --> 00:10:24,099
I...

183
00:10:25,299 --> 00:10:25,578
Well...

184
00:10:25,579 --> 00:10:26,499
Shen Yan,

185
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,578
I'm ordering you as Mrs. Huo.

186
00:10:28,579 --> 00:10:30,019
Tell me the truth.

187
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:31,578
Alright, Mrs. Huo.

188
00:10:31,579 --> 00:10:32,698
Mr. Huo was...

189
00:10:32,699 --> 00:10:34,339
He was taken by Huo Zichen.

190
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:35,499
But don't do anything reckless.

191
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:36,899
He can handle this on his own.

192
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:38,739
The most important thing now
is keeping you safe.

193
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:39,619
Please don't be rash.

194
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:40,739
You need to stay rational.

195
00:10:40,740 --> 00:10:41,219
Mr. Huo...

196
00:10:41,220 --> 00:10:42,499
Mr. Huo has a plan.

197
00:10:42,659 --> 00:10:43,379
Mrs. Huo.

198
00:10:46,140 --> 00:10:47,099
Mrs. Huo.

199
00:10:47,939 --> 00:10:48,779
Mrs. Huo!

200
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:51,180
Mrs. Huo.

201
00:10:51,359 --> 00:10:53,058
You don't even know
where Mr. Huo is. You...

202
00:10:53,059 --> 00:10:54,578
I'm not going after him.

203
00:10:54,579 --> 00:10:55,979
I'm going to find Ye Xin.

204
00:10:56,659 --> 00:10:58,660
We're the only ones who can settle this.

205
00:10:58,860 --> 00:10:59,979
You can leave now.

206
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:01,220
Mrs. Huo.

207
00:11:11,299 --> 00:11:12,540
Fine.

208
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:14,379
Just great.

209
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:17,019
You're always
the caring cousin, aren't you?

210
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:18,339
You're always the one

211
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:20,739
worrying about keeping
the family drama private.

212
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:21,940
You...

213
00:11:22,419 --> 00:11:24,979
are always the perfect,
respectable Huo Beiyan.

214
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:27,818
You get to do
all the respectable things.

215
00:11:27,819 --> 00:11:29,859
You get to play the good guy.

216
00:11:31,459 --> 00:11:32,820
What about me?

217
00:11:33,140 --> 00:11:35,099
Is everything I do just wrong?

218
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:37,139
What am I even supposed to be?

219
00:11:43,299 --> 00:11:45,300
In this whole mess,

220
00:11:45,779 --> 00:11:47,220
nobody is completely wrong.

221
00:11:51,579 --> 00:11:53,420
But nobody is completely right either.

222
00:11:57,860 --> 00:11:58,820
Zichen,

223
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:00,019
listen to me.

224
00:12:00,020 --> 00:12:01,019
If you turn around now,

225
00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:02,739
it's still not too late to fix things.

226
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:06,580
The company still has a place for you,
and the family will always be your family.

227
00:12:07,140 --> 00:12:08,418
But if you keep going down...

228
00:12:08,419 --> 00:12:09,820
Shut up!

229
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,540
I've gone too far to turn around.

230
00:12:12,860 --> 00:12:14,540
Listen up, Huo Beiyan.

231
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:16,499
All I want is to see you step down.

232
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:18,340
I want you to lose everything.

233
00:12:18,459 --> 00:12:20,418
I want to make Huo Group mine.

234
00:12:20,419 --> 00:12:21,458
I want to beat you.

235
00:12:21,459 --> 00:12:23,418
I just want to beat you for once.

236
00:12:23,419 --> 00:12:24,300
Fine!

237
00:12:26,340 --> 00:12:27,820
You want the company?

238
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,420
I'll give it to you.

239
00:12:29,579 --> 00:12:31,379
But it'll be because I gave it to you.

240
00:12:31,459 --> 00:12:32,940
Not because you won it.

241
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:37,540
You want to beat me
fair and square for once?

242
00:12:38,419 --> 00:12:39,820
I'll give you that chance.

243
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:41,979
Let's make a bet.

244
00:12:41,980 --> 00:12:42,899
How about it?

245
00:12:45,419 --> 00:12:46,499
Sure.

246
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,580
What are we betting on?

247
00:13:11,012 --> 00:13:14,786
♪What destiny brought us to meet♪

248
00:13:14,787 --> 00:13:18,107
♪Two different worlds, a love so sweet♪

249
00:13:18,112 --> 00:13:21,486
♪A wish we made
in a past life, it seems♪

250
00:13:21,487 --> 00:13:24,341
♪Destined to cross time and dream ♪

251
00:13:24,342 --> 00:13:28,182
♪Like a fairytale story told♪

252
00:13:28,262 --> 00:13:31,519
♪A gentle breeze feels so bold♪

253
00:13:31,537 --> 00:13:35,223
♪As your hair brushes past your ear♪

254
00:13:35,224 --> 00:13:37,581
♪I long to kiss your cheek, my dear♪

255
00:13:37,582 --> 00:13:41,821
♪All my longing, all my love for you♪

256
00:13:41,822 --> 00:13:44,382
♪Has never changed, it's forever true♪

257
00:13:44,824 --> 00:13:51,222
♪It's the hand of fate
that we meet again♪

258
00:13:52,024 --> 00:13:56,462
♪Let me hold you once again♪

259
00:13:56,712 --> 00:13:59,632
♪Resting against your chest♪

260
00:13:59,982 --> 00:14:05,223
♪Your warmth shines like stars at night♪

261
00:14:05,224 --> 00:14:10,023
♪Let me kiss you once again♪

262
00:14:10,024 --> 00:14:12,823
♪No reason needed♪

263
00:14:12,824 --> 00:14:15,021
♪My heart belongs to you♪

264
00:14:15,022 --> 00:14:20,742
♪I'm not afraid
to cross time to find you♪
